  <brief_title>Biomarker Testing and DNA Collection in Subjects Participating in Protocol 22001</brief_title>
  <official_title>Biomarker Testing and DNA Collection in Subjects Participating in a Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Crossover, Flexible-Dose Evaluation of the Efficacy, Safety, and Tolerability of STX209 in the Treatment of Irritability in Subjects With Fragile X Syndrome</official_title>
