  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The subjects that meet the inclusion and exclusion criteria and consent to participate in
      protocol 22001 will be offered participation in 22001A which will evaluate secreted protein
      before and after treatment with STX209 and placebo to determine if they correlate with
      effectiveness of treatment or susceptibility to treatment with STX209. These same subjects
      will also be asked to contribute a blood sample for DNA (deoxyribonucleic acid) collection.
      The investigators will study the DNA to determine if STX209 works better in people with
      specific gene variations, or to find new gene variations that predict how well STX209 works.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
